resources.string: What happens when a strawberry gets run over crossing the street? Traffic jam.
What did the left eye say to the right eye? Between you and me, something smells.
Where do young trees go to learn? Elementree school.
Don`t whistle in your house, you`ll have no money!
Breaking the dishes is a good omen, they say it`s for luck.
To cut hair during the growing moon is for good luck.
